{"product_id":"hej-the-lover-lip-balm-cactus-4-7g","title":"HEJ Organic The Lover Lip Balm Cactus 4,7g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith a lip balm, you give your lips moisture and intensive care. Unfortunately, most lip balms contain mineral oil, which acts as a film on your skin and dries it out even more. As a result, you feel the need to apply more and more cream. With Hej Lover Lip Balm, this can't happen to you! It contains 100% natural and high-quality ingredients that nourish and moisturize your lips instead of taking them away.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMakes the lips soft immediately\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for daily use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes with prickly pear seed oil, castor and argan oil\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e100% natural\/ 100% vegan\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply daily on the lips if necessary\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil [1], Rhus Verniciflua Peel Cera, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil [1], Candelilla Cera, (Euphorbia Cerifera) Wax, Butyrum (clarified butter) [1], Copernica Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax [1], Theobroma Cacao, (Cocoa) Seed Butter [1], Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil [1], Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil [1], Perfume (Fragrance) [2], Opuntia Ficus-Indica Seed Oil [1], Tocopherol [1], Glycerin[1], Limonene [2], Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Linalool [2], Citral [2], Aqua (Water), Citronellol [2], Citrus Paradisi Fruit Extract [1], Geraniol [2] 1. from controlled organic agriculture 2. from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49596728672583,"sku":null,"price":3.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-the-lover-lip-balm-cactus-47g-134587.png?v=1739897250","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/hej-the-lover-lip-balm-cactus-4-7g","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}